therefore I would be most grateful if any existing links could be 
updated to one of the new urls:

http://sourceforge.net/projects/sharpneat/
http://sharpneat.sourceforge.net/

The old site is still up - I will put a redirect page on there soon. 
Hopefully sourceforge will provide a more permanent home for SharpNEAT 
going forward.

Thanks,
